 la place qui lui revient dans les études bibliques. "--cPublisher's website.  aLatin texts with facing French translations, introduction and notes in French.00aJerome,cSaint,d-419 or 420.tPrefaces.00aBiblevCommentaries.07aBible.2fast0(OCoLC)fst01356024. 7aCommentaries.2fast0(OCoLC)fst01423723.1 aCanellis, Aline,eeditor,etranslator.4edt4trl.02iContainer of (expression):aJerome,cSaint,d-419 or 420.tPrefaces.lFrenchs(Canellis)02iContainer of (expression):aJerome,cSaint,d-419 or 420.tPrefaces.lLatins(Canellis) 0aSources chrétiennes ;vno 592.x0750-1978.  a.b90300051b02-12-18c01-31-18  addb01-31-18cmdae-ffregfr h0i1 1aBR65.J472bF7 2017z050 4g1i00052821375ldddanbjbu-fDAVIS  9Under Authority Control  aC0bNOC  aBR65.J472bF7 2017g1i00052821375j0lddda nbjb / cl. sep. s.o.o-p$0.00q-r-s-t0u0v0w0x0y.i115376252z01-31-18